data.description: Welcome to this cute 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home just minutes from Fort Cavazos and several shopping and hospitality opportunities. This home features ceramic tile throughout the entire house, wood burning fireplace, French doors leading to the dining room and kitchen. The master bedroom easily fits a king sized bed and the master bath offers double vanity sinks, his and her master closets as well as a separate tub and walk in shower.  Enjoy the cool fall weather in the closed in back porch and free up garage space by keeping the lawn equipment in the storage shed out back. Don't forget to take advantage of the newly installed solar panels at no cost to you....that's right these are being paid for at closing! This home is more than ready for new owners!
